{"tha-ap47:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap47:0.2":"Upalivagga ","tha-ap47:0.3":"Pancahatthiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap47:1.1":"“Sumedho nama sambuddho, ","tha-ap47:1.2":"gacchate antarapane; ","tha-ap47:1.3":"Okkhittacakkhu mitabhani, ","tha-ap47:1.4":"satima samvutindriyo. ","tha-ap47:2.1":"Panca uppalahatthani, ","tha-ap47:2.2":"avelattham ahamsu me; ","tha-ap47:2.3":"Tena buddham apujesim, ","tha-ap47:2.4":"pasanno sehi panibhi. ","tha-ap47:3.1":"Aropita ca te puppha, ","tha-ap47:3.2":"chadanam assu satthuno; ","tha-ap47:3.3":"Samadhimsu mahanagam, ","tha-ap47:3.4":"sissa acariyam yatha. ","tha-ap47:4.1":"Timsakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap47:4.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap47:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap47:4.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap47:5.1":"Ito visakappasate, ","tha-ap47:5.2":"ahesum panca khattiya; ","tha-ap47:5.3":"Hatthiya nama namena, ","tha-ap47:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap47:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap47:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap47:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap47:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pancahatthiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap47:8.1":"Pancahatthiyattherassapadanam pancamam. "}